---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<main class="page">
		<section class="hero">
			<p class="eyebrow">HealthAI Notes</p>
			<h1>Clear writing on AI in healthcare, without the product theater.</h1>
			<p class="lede">
				A focused site for notes, essays, and practical guidance on clinical AI, operations,
				documentation, and responsible adoption.
			</p>
			<div class="actions">
				<a class="primary" href="https://github.com/healthai-notes/healthai-notes.github.io">
					View The Repository
				</a>
				<a class="secondary" href="#focus">See The Focus Areas</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="focus" class="grid">
			<article class="card">
				<span>01</span>
				<h2>Clinical Workflow</h2>
				<p>
					Where AI actually reduces friction for clinicians, and where it adds new operational
					burden.
				</p>
			</article>
			<article class="card">
				<span>02</span>
				<h2>Documentation</h2>
				<p>
					Ambient notes, coding support, chart review, and the messy details between demos and
					real use.
				</p>
			</article>
			<article class="card">
				<span>03</span>
				<h2>Governance</h2>
				<p>
					How to evaluate model behavior, risk, privacy, and procurement without hand-waving.
				</p>
			</article>
		</section>

		<section class="feature">
			<div>
				<p class="eyebrow">Current Direction</p>
				<h2>A solid GitHub Pages starting point, ready for real content.</h2>
			</div>
			<p>
				This Astro site is now configured for GitHub Pages deployment. The next useful step is
				replacing this placeholder copy with your actual articles, profile, or newsletter links.
			</p>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	:root {
		color-scheme: light;
		--bg: #f5efe4;
		--ink: #16211d;
		--muted: #5e665f;
		--panel: rgba(255, 251, 245, 0.78);
		--line: rgba(22, 33, 29, 0.12);
		--accent: #d66c2f;
		--accent-2: #2f6b5f;
	}

	body {
		font-family: Georgia, 'Iowan Old Style', 'Palatino Linotype', 'Book Antiqua', serif;
		background:
			radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(214, 108, 47, 0.22), transparent 34%),
			radial-gradient(circle at right 18%, rgba(47, 107, 95, 0.16), transparent 28%),
			linear-gradient(180deg, #f7f1e7 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
		color: var(--ink);
	}

	.page {
		max-width: 1120px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 72px 24px 96px;
	}

	.hero,
	.feature,
	.card {
		backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
		background: var(--panel);
		border: 1px solid var(--line);
		box-shadow: 0 18px 60px rgba(51, 44, 32, 0.08);
	}

	.hero {
		padding: 48px;
		border-radius: 28px;
	}

	.eyebrow {
		margin: 0 0 12px;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.18em;
		font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		color: var(--accent-2);
	}

	h1 {
		max-width: 10ch;
		margin: 0;
		font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6.4rem);
		line-height: 0.92;
	}

	.lede {
		max-width: 38rem;
		margin: 24px 0 0;
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: var(--muted);
	}

	.actions {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 14px;
		margin-top: 28px;
	}

	.actions a {
		text-decoration: none;
		padding: 14px 18px;
		border-radius: 999px;
		font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.primary {
		background: var(--ink);
		color: #f7f1e7;
	}

	.secondary {
		border: 1px solid var(--line);
		color: var(--ink);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
	}

	.grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 18px;
		margin-top: 22px;
	}

	.card {
		padding: 24px;
		border-radius: 22px;
	}

	.card span {
		display: inline-block;
		font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
		color: var(--accent);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.18em;
	}

	h2 {
		margin: 14px 0 8px;
		font-size: 1.55rem;
	}

	.card p,
	.feature p {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--muted);
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.feature {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr;
		gap: 24px;
		margin-top: 22px;
		padding: 32px;
		border-radius: 24px;
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.grid,
		.feature {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.hero {
			padding: 32px 24px;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.page {
			padding: 24px 16px 64px;
		}

		h1 {
			max-width: none;
		}
	}
</style>
